<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - ARV Assisted.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - ARV Assisted.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- PaineWebber said it downgraded ARV Assisted Living Inc to neutral from attractive.</p>
<p>-- Earlier on Wednesday, ARV Assisted posted third quarter earnings of $0.03 a share on revenues of $23.8 million, compared with earnings of nil on revenues of $9.5 million last year.</p>
<p>-- Additional details were not immediately available.</p>
<p>-- ARV lost 1/8 to 9-1/4 in morning trading.</p>
